snippet.title: Lone Survivor - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Out now!  Purchase for $10 at http://www.lonesurvivor.co.uk (DRM-free updates for life) or on Steam http://store.steampowered.com/agecheck/app/209830/

Play the online demo here: http://www.kongregate.com/games/superflat/lone-survivor-demo

Music is "Sleep Forever" by Jasper Byrne, from the Lone Survivor Original Soundtrack, available for purchase at: http://www.spacerecordings.bandcamp.com

Thankyou to Anna Anthropy for use of the 'Slanted' typeface.
